---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Ed Barlow — Ed Barlow">
  <section class="home-intro">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <h1 class="home-name">Ed Barlow</h1>
      <div class="home-body">
<p><strong>AI Assisted Developer</strong> with several ai assisted project completions. I can one shot small and mid sized projects with prebuilt guidance and can manage many projects using Generic Enterprise Manager V2</p>
<p><strong>Principal Engineer/Director</strong> at major hedge funds, investment banks, and startups </p>
<p><strong>Writing, Game And Free Software Developer</strong></p>
<ul>
<li> Multi Player Free Game Conquer - Adventure Game Templar</li>
<li> (very popular) Sybase Developer and Shareware Web Site</li>
<ul>
<li> (very popular) Ed Barlows Sybase and Sql Server Procedure Library</li>
<li> (very popular) Ed Barlows Extended Sybase and Sql Server Backup Scripts</li>
<li> Sybase Developer Conference Speaker </li>
</ul>
<li> Book: Process Based Enginnering Best Practices</li>
<li> Generic Enterprise Manager - Effectively manage hundreds of databases / thousands of hosts </li>
</ul>

<p><strong>AI Methedology</strong></p>
<p>My Methedology is changing as AI technology practices change. To these I integrate the <strong>best practices</strong>, <strong>workflow</strong>, and <strong>metrics</strong> from my Book <strong>Process Based Database Administration</strong> with the scaled <strong>Automation and Monitoring</strong> tooling details of my Generic Enterprise Manager.</p>
<h2>Feature Workflow</h2>
<p><img src="/webcloudstudio/diagrams/v3-feature-workflow.png"> </p>
<h2>Project Definition</h2>
<p><img src="/webcloudstudio/diagrams/v3-project-definition.png" ></p>
<h2>AI Workflow</h2>
<p><img src="/webcloudstudio/diagrams/v3-ai-workflow.png" ></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .home-intro { padding: 4rem 0 3rem; }

    .home-name {
      font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      margin: 0 0 2rem;
    }

    .home-body { max-width: 860px; }

    .home-body p {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.75;
      margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
    }

    .home-body h2 {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text);
      margin: 2rem 0 0.75rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    }

    .home-body ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .home-body li {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      padding-left: 1.2rem;
      position: relative;
    }

    .home-body li::before {
      content: '—';
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      color: var(--accent);
    }

    .home-body strong { color: var(--text); font-weight: 600; }

    .home-body em {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-style: italic;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
